description: Outline hybrid planning application for the comprehensive redevelopment of the whole site following the demolition of existing buildings and structures excluding the pumphouse, dockside heritage features and flood defence infrastructure to provide up to 819 residential units (including affordable housing) and up to 3,617 sq.m of office (Class B1), 1,353 sq.m of retail (Class A1 to A4), 703 sq.m of community (Class D1) and 417 sq.m of leisure (Class D2) of flexible (GIA) floorspace;
